title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Dramatically increasing your earning potential is a top priority today. Its normal to speculate or fantasize about obtaining abundance and wealth, whether through winning the lottery or launching a sensational idea that goes viral. But wishing and hoping for an unrealistic miracle does nothing to raise your financial standing. Instead of yearning for instant prosperity, grant yourself permission to dare for more by desiring less. Imam Ali taught, The richest of the rich is one who is not a prisoner to greed. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
